virhepalaute__info: The feedback will be sent to Public Service Info, which processes all feedback related to Suomi.fi identification.
virhepalaute__lomake__mobiili__legend: Which operator’s mobile certificate did you use?
virhepalaute__lomake__palvelu__additiona: If necessary, complement the service name and add the location if you used the service of a certain area
virhepalaute__lomake__selain__valinta: If you used some other browser, please give the browser name and version
virhepalaute__lomake__tunnistustapa: Which method of identification did you use?
virhepalaute__lomake__virheaika__legend: When did the error occur (time as accurately as possible)
virhepalaute__lomake__virhekoodi__legend: Which error code is given in the error message?
virhepalaute__lomake__virhekoodi__valint: Does the error message contain an error code?
virhepalaute__lomake__virhekuvaus__legen: Explain shortly what you were doing
virhepalaute__lomake__virheviesti__legen: What the text on the error page says?
virhepalaute__lomake__yhteystiedot_ei: No, thank you (the feedback will be processed anonymously)
virhepalaute__lomake__yhteystiedot_label: Would you like the person processing the feedback to contact you?
virhepalaute__lomake__yhteystiedot_legen: If you would like us to respond to your feedback, please include your e-mail address. You may also submit feedback anonymously.
virhepalaute__p1: You can use this form to report an error that occurred in connection with Suomi.fi-identification. Your notification will be processed by Public Service Info, which provides advice on the use of public administration e-services and identifying yourself in them.
virhepalaute__virhe__puuttuu: Please check that you have entered mandatory fields
virhepalaute__virhe__viesti_puuttuu: Please check that you have entered a feedback message
virhepalaute__virhe__virheviesti_puuttuu: Please check that you have entered an error report
